(33927, 'Zathrotrue 500 mg 6 f.c. tabs.', 'زاثروترو 500 مجم 6 قرص', '65', '96', 'Azithromycin', 'October pharma', 'Tab', 'أقراص', '', 'Antibiotic.macrolide', '500 mg', 'Azithromycin should be used only to treat or prevent infections that are proven or strongly suspected to be caused by susceptible bacteria in order to prevent the development antimicrobial resistance and maintain the efficacy of azithromycin [FDA label].
